<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        /* Common styles for all emails */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4a5568;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border-left: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-right: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #718096;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4a5568;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .credentials {
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        h1 {
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }
        .important {
            color: #e53e3e;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="email-wrapper">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>Your New Password - Church Management System</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
                
                <h2>Your Password Has Been Reset</h2>
                
                <p>Your password for the Church Management System for "<strong>{{churchName}}</strong>" has been reset. You can now access the system with the following credentials:</p>
                
                <div class="credentials">
                    <p><strong>Email/Username:</strong> {{email}}</p>
                    <p><strong>New Password:</strong> {{password}}</p>
                </div>
                
                <p class="important">Please change your password immediately after logging in for security purposes.</p>
                
                <p>You can access the church dashboard by clicking the button below:</p>
                
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <a href="{{loginLink}}" class="button">Access Dashboard</a>
                </div>
                
                <p>If you did not request this password reset, please contact your church administrator immediately as your account may have been compromised.</p>
                
                <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact your church administrator or our support team.</p>
                
                <p>Blessings,<br>
                Church Management System Team</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} Church Management System. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p>This email was sent to {{email}}. If you believe this email was sent to you in error, please contact your church administrator.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>